    "title": "Changelog media pipeline rebuilt around Browser Use",
    "intro": "Today's nightly is a single large refactor: the old Playwright- and Browserbase-driven demo screenshot pipeline has been retired in favor of a leaner Browser Use planning flow, and a new capture-auth path lands in the server and interface to support it. Net result is a significant code reduction (~20k lines removed) and a cleaner foundation for automated changelog media.",
